msgid "Surprised Man"
msgstr "Uomo Sorpreso"

msgctxt "476"
msgid "Talk_Think"
msgstr "Talk_Think"

msgctxt "72_Surprised Man"
msgid "Man, that was amazin'. Never seen that many fancy black cars in a row."
msgstr ""
"Mamma mia, che roba pazzesca! Non ho mai visto così tante macchine nere di "
"lusso tutte in fila."

msgctxt "84_Surprised Man"
msgid ""
"I wonder where they were going. Maybe they were shootin' a commercial or "
"something."
msgstr ""
"Chissà dove andavano. Forse stavano girando uno spot pubblicitario o roba "
"del genere."
